data.text:
Actress Felicite Wouassi, left, kisses director Francois Dupeyron, during the photocall of their movie "Aide-toi et le ciel t'aidera" (Help yourself and Heaven will help you) at the third edition of the Rome Film Festival, in Rome, Monday, Oct. 27, 2008. The third edition of the Rome film festival is scheduled to run until Oct. 31. (AP Photo/Andrew Medichini)
